$AOPEN_LINK
Gosub AVARIABLES
Link [POH] With
& [POP]POP0 ~= [POH]POHNUM,
& [POQ]POQ0 ~= [POP]POHNUM;[POP]POPLIN;[POP]POPSEQ,
